What you need to know:

Staging the Rally Monte Carlo successfully is the fillip the WRC needs in an unknown world health status.  But as Matton was quoted saying: “There are no guarantees because of Covid.”“Of course, there will be constraints and changes, but if we can achieve an event like this (Monte Carlo), then we can achieve more and more events during the year ahead, although it is obviously disappointing that Rally Sweden won’t be able to take place,” said Matton.